THIRD-PARTY LICENSES
====================

This file lists all third-party dependencies used by Glass and their licenses.
Generated by cargo-license.

NOTE: self_cell is dual-licensed as "Apache-2.0 OR GPL-2.0". Glass uses it
under the Apache-2.0 license, which is compatible with MIT. The GPL-2.0
option is NOT exercised.

NOTE: No OpenSSL linkage exists in this project. On Windows, SChannel is used
for TLS (via native-tls/rustls). On Unix, rustls is used.

